targets.query:
from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "in" or r["_field"] == "out")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "delta")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "in_delta" or r["_field"] == "out_delta")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["temperature"] == "engine" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_l" or r["temperature"] == "radiator_r")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "CAN")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "0x609")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "flow_left" or r["_field"] == "flow_right")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "left" or r["_field"] == "right")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["radiator"] == "heat")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "heat_from_engine" or r["_field"] == "heat_theoretical")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["engine"] == "heat")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "Coolant fan")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["engine"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: max)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value == 1 }))

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "RPM")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["engine"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "MAP")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["engine"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "temp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["oil"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "clt")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ecumaster"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

total_number = () => {
  row = from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["value"] == "range")
    |> count()  
    |> last() 
    |> findRecord(fn: (key) => true, idx:0)
  return float(v: row._value)
    
}


from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "TPS" and r["value"] == "range")
  |> duplicate(column: "_value", as: "new_column")
  |> group(columns: ["new_column"])
  |> count()
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: float(v: r._value) /total_number() * 100.0}))

from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "engine")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "TPS")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["engine"] == "raw")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)
